{
  "texts": [
    "An innovative approach introduced in Li et al. (2022) utilizes an autonomous control method based on the DDPG to effectively mitigate issues associated with under-voltage load shedding.",
    "Also adaptive under voltage load shedding and emergency control schemes using deep reinforcement learning (DRL) is proposed in Huang Q. et al. (2020).",
    "Similarly, Chen et al. (2021) presents a model-free emergency frequency control strategy, leveraging reinforcement learning to navigate the complexities of such scenarios.",
    "Notably, it introduces a multi-Q-learning-based method to limit the number of emergency scenarios that should be addressed when designing the system.",
    "To learn the optimal solutions for identified general emergency scenarios, DDPG algorithm is adopted."
  ]
}